                <h1>Discover the Rich History of Massage Therapy</h1>
                <p>Massage therapy has ancient roots, dating back over 5,000 years to civilizations like China and Egypt. Initially used for healing and relaxation, techniques evolved through time, influenced by cultures worldwide. Today, various forms exist, such as Swedish and deep tissue, valued for pain relief and stress reduction.</p>
